text: Dalbergia hancei is a species of liana, with the Vietnamese name (dây) trắc Hance. The genus Dalbergia is placed in the subfamily Faboideae and tribe Dalbergieae; no subspecies are listed in the Catalogue of Life. == References == Heald,J., 1992 Specimen in Herb.
